# Integration tests load repo-root home_assistant.secrets.env automatically (no need to ``source``).
# Override path with env: HOME_ASSISTANT_SECRETS_PATH=/path/to/file
#
# 1) cp home_assistant.secrets.env.example home_assistant.secrets.env   (at repo root)
# 2) Edit home_assistant.secrets.env once (IP + token); skip PASTE_YOUR_* placeholders.
# 3) From repo root:
#      pytest services/core/PlatformDriverAgent/tests/test_home_assistant.py
#
# Optional: still use shell helper or manual export:
#      set -a && source services/core/PlatformDriverAgent/tests/load_home_assistant_secrets.env && set +a
